ZH: 我很理解你的感受。
EN: I understand how you feel.

ZH: 请你理解我的处境。
EN: Please understand my situation.

ZH: 我很难理解这个概念。
EN: I find it difficult to understand this concept.

ZH: 他正在努力理解这个难题。
EN: He is working hard to understand this difficult problem.

ZH: 请给我时间来理解你的观点。
EN: Please give me time to understand your point of view.

ZH: 父母经常很难理解孩子的心情。
EN: Parents often have difficulty understanding their children's feelings.

ZH: 她一直在试图理解他的决定。
EN: She has been trying to understand his decision.

ZH: 我知道你很想要被理解。
EN: I know you want to be understood.

ZH: 这个问题还需要更多时间来理解。
EN: This issue needs more time to be understood.

ZH: 请不要误解我的意图。
EN: Please do not misunderstand my intentions.

ZH: 他很善于理解别人的需求。
EN: He is very good at understanding other people's needs.

ZH: 我很重视彼此的理解。
EN: I value mutual understanding.

ZH: 让我们共同努力来增进理解。
EN: Let's work together to enhance understanding.

ZH: 请尽量理解我的立场。
EN: Please try to understand my position.

ZH: 我们需要更多的沟通来促进理解。
EN: We need more communication to promote understanding.

ZH: 他很欣慰地看到对方理解他的立场。
EN: He was pleased to see the other party understand his position.

ZH: 请你试着理解他的处境。
EN: Please try to understand his situation.

ZH: 只有通过沟通才能得到真正的理解。
EN: Only through communication can we achieve true understanding.

ZH: 请给我一些时间来适应和理解。
EN: Please give me some time to adapt and understand.

ZH: 我们经常需要多角度来理解一个问题。
EN: We often need multiple perspectives to understand an issue.
